data.description:
VIEWING APPOINTMENTS WILL BE SETUP AFTER AN APPLICATION IS RECEIVED

Available Now - 2Bed 2.5 Bath 1250sqft home on 40 Acres in Pioneer, CA in the private Sherwood Drive area.

FOLLOW DIRECTIONS BELOW TO APPLY

FREE APPLICATIONS

Ultimate in privacy and living within nature on an entire 40 acres! Bring your horses and pets! Home is a cozy 2 story with 2 Bedrooms, 2.5 Bathrooms, on 40 acres with trails and Ashland creek running through it. Enjoy vast open outdoors with no neighbors nearby. Open floor plan with great room concept. Enjoy your own clean well water. Close to Golfing, Skiing and Casinos. Only 30 Minutes away from Jackson, 1.5 hours away from Lake Tahoe and Sacramento.

Perimeter of property is NOT fenced and is densely wooded with private hiking trails all around the property.

DSL Internet is available through Volcano Communications internet company at your own cost.

Rent is $2195 / month with $4000 deposit.

NO Smoking allowed, Pets on a case by case basis and require pet deposit.

You pay for PGE Electricity and Propane refills, water is supplied by onsite private well and onsite septic system.

**RENTAL REQUIREMENTS**
Our requirements are as follows for renting the home:
1)	Verifiable NET (take home) income of 2x the rent ($4390 / month)
2)	No evictions or judgments from a landlord in the last 5 years.
3)	Current checking account
4)	We use automatic rent collection via ACH, if you prefer to send in rent manually then add $150/month for manual processing.
5)	Deposit is $4000, 1st months rent and deposit due at lease signing.

APPLICATION INSTRUCTIONS

1) Reply to this AD and TYPE your EMAIL ADDRESS so that we can email you an application and instructions. 
2) Interior Viewing appointment will be set AFTER your application is received AND approved.
3) Any questions not answered with the above information please email us.

Bobby S. Khieu, Broker BRE:01759226 NMLS:251619
Blue Enlightenment Real Estate Group BRE: 01759226

Application is FREE from us (dont use zillow application). Tenant responsible for all Electric, Propane, Trash and all day to day household and gardening maintenance of the property during lease term.
